{"word":"βάρος","slug":"βάρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βάρος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαρύς'><el>βαρύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>weight</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a weight, burden, load</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>a heavy weight</i>, <el>πημονῆς, συμφορᾶς β.</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; then alone for <i>grief, misery</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>βάρος ἔχειν</el> <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>IV. </b><i>abundance</i>, <el>πλούτου, ὄλβου</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}